com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model

Class Device

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.common.model.Device
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Device
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Model class that represents JSON structure of Kontakt.io device.

    Device is a property of Manager. It acts also as a container for Action objects and may be assigned to certain Venue. We can obtain devices via KontaktCloud.

    To create new instance of this class, please use Device.Builder.
